{
  "stem": "5644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a market which was from 1900, 1900.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a market taken by the Polish socialist ruled around there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was an-- that was like an-- no, that was a market for everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But underground people used it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I explained why they used it there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, you'd be very, very safe with the boys you dealt with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is the funny part of it, how that start there, how you worked there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You went into a man which called Johnny, John, Janic, or Bolic or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You ask him, you want to buy the guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything is all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Arrange with you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very honest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could pay money ahead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I knew that most of the boys, even that wasn't in organization, they suspect him of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew that with an organization, it's not good to do something wrong because you can be killed for it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you come the next day and you're happy-- or two days later-- and you're happy with what you bought from him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you call him again, Janic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he looked at you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am the boy which bought from you-- which bought from you from-- you want to stop it?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wouldn't know-- he wouldn't recognize.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't want to say that is Janic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are Janic?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am not Janic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am Zbyszek.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, but I-- he said, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I haven't seen you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know who you are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So to walk away from him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As soon as you start to walk away, he said, but what do you want, actually?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
